"<strong>Flow 2: Point of sale - Regular flow with Buy one get one free "
"product</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຂັ້ນຕອນທີ 2: ຈຸດຂາຍ (POS) - ຂັ້ນຕອນປົກກະຕິ ພ້ອມໂປຣໂມຊັ່ນ ຊື້ໜຶ່ງແຖມໜຶ່ງ</strong>"

#. module: fmcg_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fmcg_store.welcome_article_body
